{"tid":1979021,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中文dse 弱雞的提示","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T02:30:35.000Z","uid":79005,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac39732dda4f6f6f16f0c1df39e2d2b584022c3","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"中文dse注意事項<br />\n卷一:<br />\n小心冗文，文句不通，矛盾，避免大包圍、直背範文欠解釋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用詞宜  精準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文言文字詞解釋分數必拎 溫熟D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解釋文言文句子時，小心抽出關鍵字，數分數。<br />\n撞到三色判斷題請打醒精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />考評局好陰濕 邏輯一定要清楚<br />\n全部題目睇一次先，你個腦會幫你無意識run咁d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間分配<br />\n<br />\n卷二:<br />\n切忌行文兇暴、怨天尤人、無病呻吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n審題宜清晰，每字每標點均可能影響你對題目的理解！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫前宜有腦圖大綱<br />\n最好先有一中心思想、高尚而雅正的主旨，如樂天知命、積極向上、有關傳統美德為佳。反諷、風趣表達，對社會現象的針砭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好曬冷時例、史例，唔係考緊中史、通識，而是文字表達、鋪排組織能力的一次考驗。<br />\n沒有好的文字也未嘗不能高分，所言清昕、表達飽滿、立意高潔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卷三:<br />\n唔好發夢、red bull, 咖啡可考慮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心耳機失靈、後備電池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n善用螢光筆、兩旁空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一題多是歸納整段錄音各人的說話內容、立場、宜聽的過程中留意。<br />\n好寫的筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要過份托展，浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心格式，第二部分錄音最尾多數會出現提你有咩格式要加、行文語氣注意事項<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卷四: 今年取消咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年一年拎2、一年3 我講野真係1999果D人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以冇咩建議。<br />\n15年拎四, 16年拎過五... 今年再試多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n較定生理時鐘喇記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97640f24de1ff4d5a89b1aaa27c0c1163cc2a626","tid":1979021,"uid":330227,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"飲咖啡／奶茶會肚痛嗰啲<br />\n記住唔好挑戰自己消化系統嘅能耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba79e44e4dd700d4fa3c7b19770979267b2d55c","tid":1979021,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"12年表示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73895708fbfe11a739f7350d28ff07dec1532c76","tid":1979021,"uid":201414,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"想當年有條撚樣考考下瀨撚左屎 好撚臭 開撚曬窗都唔掂 我想問番當年考中交既瀨屎仔 屌你啦 忍住臭做卷慘過吔屎"},{"pid":"256fa001a01d2809563dbdd4dc513b8f5907940f","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73895708fbfe11a739f7350d28ff07dec1532c76","tid":1979021,"uid":201414,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"想當年有條撚樣考考下瀨撚左屎 好撚臭 開撚曬窗都唔掂 我想問番當年考中交既瀨屎仔 屌你啦 忍住臭做卷慘過吔屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇啲咩建議俾今年啲考生吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d910044b328a4cbb1fbec64e180d814a9786cd57","tid":1979021,"uid":308332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"短而精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />卷二tips真心好啱 我就係冇咩靚文筆都有5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 此post要每年回帶"},{"pid":"9341f7723a123f7e587808ae9bf6eddd616c506b","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"推多一次 應該都冇咩人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ea67338575d9f1955a8592504e8e22c39ceaa","tid":1979021,"uid":58201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"唉 想當年卷二戇鳩衰衝動睇錯題目<br />\n最後2咗"},{"pid":"b4e803759fea758ee64fd8592bfc8071ec5a7628","tid":1979021,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc4ea67338575d9f1955a8592504e8e22c39ceaa","tid":1979021,"uid":58201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"唉 想當年卷二戇鳩衰衝動睇錯題目<br />\n最後2咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ecc83edf5533137f9e200d0b558677b4748d83","tid":1979021,"uid":177620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ac39732dda4f6f6f16f0c1df39e2d2b584022c3","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"中文dse注意事項<br />\n卷一:<br />\n小心冗文，文句不通，矛盾，避免大包圍、直背範文欠解釋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用詞宜  精準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文言文字詞解釋分數必拎 溫熟D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解釋文言文句子時，小心抽出關鍵字，數分數。<br />\n撞到三色判斷題請打醒精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />考評局好陰濕 邏輯一定要清楚<br />\n全部題目睇一次先，你個腦會幫你無意識run咁d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間分配<br />\n<br />\n卷二:<br />\n切忌行文兇暴、怨天尤人、無病呻吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n審題宜清晰，每字每標點均可能影響你對題目的理解！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫前宜有腦圖大綱<br />\n最好先有一中心思想、高尚而雅正的主旨，如樂天知命、積極向上、有關傳統美德為佳。反諷、風趣表達，對社會現象的針砭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好曬冷時例、史例，唔係考緊中史、通識，而是文字表達、鋪排組織能力的一次考驗。<br />\n沒有好的文字也未嘗不能高分，所言清昕、表達飽滿、立意高潔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卷三:<br />\n唔好發夢、red bull, 咖啡可考慮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心耳機失靈、後備電池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n善用螢光筆、兩旁空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一題多是歸納整段錄音各人的說話內容、立場、宜聽的過程中留意。<br />\n好寫的筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要過份托展，浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心格式，第二部分錄音最尾多數會出現提你有咩格式要加、行文語氣注意事項<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卷四: 今年取消咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年一年拎2、一年3 我講野真係1999果D人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以冇咩建議。<br />\n15年拎四, 16年拎過五... 今年再試多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n較定生理時鐘喇記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"我嗰時卷二寫&ldquo;憤怒&rdquo;寫到好多怨氣好尖酸<br />\n之後5*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遇到伯樂"},{"pid":"751b489ff09ffd29b1d992460e47850c5c012c12","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"好似抒情咁<br />\n唔好就咁寫感受 或寫完件事講感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾情夾景 一時心 一時景 似有非有嘅抒情 令人望落有餘韻 唔知你有冇言外之意，增加可讀性，但唔好太高級，marker睇唔明會下年見。<br />\n講下古討十九首啲例子 扮唔倒唔好夾硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子：<br />\n迢迢牽牛星，皎皎河漢女。 典故<br />\n纖纖擢素手，札札弄機杼。 故人形象、行為<br />\n終日不成章，泣涕零如雨； 表情<br />\n河漢清且淺，相去復幾許！景<br />\n盈盈一水間，脈脈不得語。情景<br />\n<br />\n全詩冇講自己的感受，但托物、托事、托典故、托景。托物寄意，融情於景，常可收意想不到的文章韻味。<br />\n弱雞例子：我敲著鍵盤，那聲音&hellip;&hellip;.遠在千里深山村中的外婆，應也同樣踏著織布機，達達達，以前她織布時，我在邊搖著小鼓，達咚達，兩音差距，一無情機械，一深邃靈聲，卻久久撓在耳邊。<br />\n就字面睇，只係講緊我做緊野、外婆織緊布，但讀者會感受到應該係對外婆的思念，但情感委婉、立意雅正，類似係咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再舉多個咩叫委婉而情深的例子，呢首講緊一位孝子出遠門，佢寫對家人的思念，唔係直講，而係用家人思念佢的角度，自然收到家庭天倫之貴的感情及思念家人的情。<br />\n陟彼岵兮，瞻望父兮。父曰：嗟！予子行役，夙夜無已。上慎旃哉，猶來！無止！<br />\n陟彼屺兮，瞻望母兮。母曰：嗟！予季行役，夙夜無寐。上慎旃哉，猶來！無棄！<br />\n陟彼岡兮，瞻望兄兮。兄曰：嗟！予弟行役，夙夜必偕。上慎旃哉，猶來！無死！ <br />\n簡單d黎講即係 唔好灑狗血，一係就做豪放派，兩者都唔同嫁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179f35bf760a7099538d570336fdcb37638c8596","tid":1979021,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dba79e44e4dd700d4fa3c7b19770979267b2d55c","tid":1979021,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"12年表示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"10 年表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc4e7606e051fc4fe51e2cb42c10b9dadee41e4","tid":1979021,"uid":213217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"中文真係on9<br />\n<br />\nfirst take : 55445<br />\nsecond: 33344<br />\nthird:  54342<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804833c478ee62432498489c70e839995d33e9ac","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"全部過來人圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都好嘅 冇現屆代表咩？即係成班乖仔溫緊書 唔上連登囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337463504936fa03c916a52c0f4827b5ee8b5154","tid":1979021,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"卷一我果陣係一定要大包圍架喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知而家啦<br />\n但果陣長答 段落大鋼你唔寫勁多係含得架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b4f95d12c31003c05e39d3dcd8c601cfa3e9af","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337463504936fa03c916a52c0f4827b5ee8b5154","tid":1979021,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"卷一我果陣係一定要大包圍架喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知而家啦<br />\n但果陣長答 段落大鋼你唔寫勁多係含得架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"或者咁講 大包圍唔好包到有矛盾同影響marker理解啦<br />\n太多冗文會扣分 有冗文 唔影響意思都唔扣嘅 <br />\n大包圍 會有寫多錯多嘅風險"},{"pid":"2b3d2f28de5ebc69b5f60a7949c43431bb6e18e9","tid":1979021,"uid":207799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"thx! 學到野"},{"pid":"5a7ad963f9087350374801a45c77ff4488d1bde2","tid":1979021,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb9631e510f76b4dda2db42450a4b154da222a7","tid":1979021,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"今日講下綜合先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1ac2860ef42e0a33fa66abcd814263b943f112","tid":1979021,"uid":199441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"中文on99運氣卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}